管镜检查，导致三个月内发生 2 例患者死亡事件，事发后孟婕伪造医疗文书，要求其他医生签字担责。此外，举报者还反映孟婕「暗箱操作」绩效分配、私设小金库、财务不公开、打压排挤同事等问题。 8 月 9 日，澎湃新闻记者来到湘雅三医院了解情况，未能见到孟婕。呼吸科多名工作人员婉拒了采访。当天下午，湘雅三医院党委办工作人员向记者介绍，医院方面正在核实相关情况。 %3A%2F%2Ffinance.sina.cn%2F2023-08-10%2Fdetail-imzfsize0239342.d.html&autocallup=no&isfromsina=yes"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-b792dfa84d344eabdbf3510f3d49f198_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "21 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/616558620"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ig+iH/fvHmqMLEAMaCDk5MjkzMTQ3INv60KYGMAA4aUArcgk2MTY1NTg2MjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1691741374.902830", "card_id": "Q_616606042", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 8}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "多地公布医药领域腐败问题集中整治举报方式，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "近日，全国医药领域腐败问题集中整治的话题持续引发热议。北京、重庆、海南、云南、四川等多地公布集中整治举报方式。（中新社微信公众号）涉医药反腐，多地公布举报方式！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-0aa016af5d3131d8e085d1cc5dea3539_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "21 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/616606042"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIg+iH/fvHmqMLEAMaCDk5MzAzNjk3INXC0qYGMAA4DkAscgk2MTY2MDYwNDJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1691741374.903482", "card_id": "Q_616512909", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 2023LPL 冒泡赛 EDG1:3WBG，Theshy 选手的表现？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-ee66012bddc2fe7c129aaa6ced33677e_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "20 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/616512909"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ig+iH/fvHmqMLEAMaCDk5MjgzMDA3IJvZzqYGMAA4OUAtcgk2MTY1MTI5MDl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1691741374.903929", "card_id": "Q_615962341", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 101}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "主动暴露弱点会拉近社交距离吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "沈奕斐分享了自己「暴露弱点」拉近社交距离的故事。高中时沈奕斐性格很张扬，有一次同学们让她示范跳舞，她虽然完全不会舞蹈也上去「随便扭」，说实话扭的非常丑，但自此暴露自己的弱点后，发现同学们反而愿意接受她了。你有过这种经历吗？正片指路：25:40 社会时钟能打破吗？｜EP02 荒野会谈"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-65c942ff4dc29f948ae6c25d2ce8bd9b_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "19 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/615962341"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ig+iH/fvHmqMLEAMaCDk5MTYwNjg4IOzNvqYGMAA46wFALnIJNjE1OTYyMzQxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "47_1691741374.904737", "card_id": "Q_615810211", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么电影机都是残幅，相机随便一万的就能上全画幅？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "其实可以算是一个问题，就是电影机使用全画幅的技术的困难难在什么地方了。 首先，画幅理论上应该是越大约好。 但像那些相对比较便宜的相机能够采用全画幅，说明装备全画幅应该不会是成本很大的事。但电影机全画幅和残辅价格差距却特别大。说明改变电影机的传感器大小有技术困难或者别的成本上的问题存在。 其次电影机是工业化的精细产品，肯定追求合理价格内的最高水平，他们肯定也知道全画幅比残辅好。也算证实了对于电影机来说实施全画幅跟相机的全画幅性质和技术水平不一样。那这个不一样具体是不一样到哪了。造成这种情况的原因是什么。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-3f609d57dbf6fdf1c1db34cf08a6397b_qhd.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "19 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/615810211"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ig+iH/fvHmqMLEAMaCDk5MTI2NzAzIL3ruKYGMAA4RUAvcgk2MTU4MTAy